<p data-pp-blocktype="copy" data-pp-id="99.0">In the meantime, construction has started at the old Mount Vernon News building, which is being turned into an academic hub for a local university. The building will be named after Rastin’s stepson, a former president of Ariel Corporation.</p>
        
    
        
